of deja vu that I've had lately.

324
00:16:31,790 --> 00:16:36,050
Is it possible that other people
across the world feel this, too?

325
00:16:36,160 --> 00:16:40,960
It doesn't seem that way.
You and I are a special case.

326
00:16:41,730 --> 00:16:44,030
It appears that the people who
are closest to Miss Suzumiya...

327
00:16:44,160 --> 00:16:47,190
are able to sense
this strangeness.

328
00:16:47,470 --> 00:16:50,960
What about Haruhi? Does she
sense any of this at all?

329
00:16:51,110 --> 00:16:56,570
Not at all, it seems. It would
probably be bad for us if she did.

330
00:16:57,640 --> 00:17:03,110
However, I believe that there is one
person who remembers everything,

331
00:17:03,250 --> 00:17:06,950
more than the deja vu
that we do.

332
00:17:08,190 --> 00:17:12,720
That's an awfully unhappy thought.
And who would that be?

333
00:17:12,990 --> 00:17:15,790
I think you know,
even without my saying.

334
00:17:16,600 --> 00:17:21,400
I believe that the Thought Entity, which
transcends time and space, would.

335
00:17:23,300 --> 00:17:26,930
- Is that right, Nagato?
- It is.

336
00:17:27,070 --> 00:17:30,600
- You remember all of it?
- Right.

337
00:17:30,710 --> 00:17:35,080
So, how many times have we repeated
all of this, this time?

338
00:17:36,980 --> 00:17:41,720
This is the 15,513th time.

339
00:17:45,190 --> 00:17:48,560
15,513?

340
00:17:48,700 --> 00:17:54,600
What do you mean by 15,513?
Nagato, what are you saying?

341
00:17:57,070 --> 00:17:59,270
Are you serious?

342
00:17:59,410 --> 00:18:00,900
I am.

343
00:18:01,040 --> 00:18:06,210
You're saying that we've done the
exact same things that many times?

344
00:18:06,350 --> 00:18:08,840
They're not all guaranteed
to happen.

345
00:18:09,420 --> 00:18:10,780
Which means?

346
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:15,820
Out of 15,513 repetitions,
there are two occasions,

347
00:18:15,960 --> 00:18:20,660
#2,391 and #11,054, where we
did not go to a Bon festival.

348
00:18:21,130 --> 00:18:23,430
A pattern where we did
go to a Bon festival,

349
00:18:23,560 --> 00:18:27,160
but did not go to a goldfish scooping
stand, occurred 437 times.

350
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:30,730
We've had a part-time job
9,031 times, and in those instances,

351
00:18:30,870 --> 00:18:33,070
we have done six different
kinds of jobs.

352
00:18:33,340 --> 00:18:36,870
In addition to handing out balloons,
