We could see
the first dream

435
00:24:23,790 --> 00:24:26,120
hajimete no yume ga mieru
That we had when
we were born

436
00:24:26,230 --> 00:24:31,100
doushiyouka tte
nayanda koto mo
Worrying about
"what do I do?"

437
00:24:31,230 --> 00:24:34,830
Ima omoeba waraeru hodo
datta yo ne
Is laughable when I
think about it now

438
00:24:35,040 --> 00:24:37,270
